name: Walnut
description:
Features
:  Holds up 15kg OR 2-3 grocery bags 
:  Light weight 100% Nylon fabric
:  Fits over your shoulder
:  Re-enforced seams for added strength & durability 
:  Designed in Australia
:  Wide straps for comfort, disperses weight evenly
:  Gusseted base which allows square items to sit flat! 
:  Water resistant
:  Use your pouch to store your keys, loose coins or mobile

Size
:  Folds flat into a 4” x 5” pouch weighing 50 grams 
:  Bag dimensions 25” high/ 15” wide/ 5” deep 


All prices $AUD
